Properties.commandText:
CREATE TABLE [Books] (
    [Id] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [Author] nvarchar(32) NOT NULL,
    [Title] nvarchar(90) NOT NULL,
    [Description] nvarchar(180) NOT NULL,
    [CreatedAt] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Books] PRIMARY KEY ([Id])
);

CREATE TABLE [Customers] (
    [Id] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [FirstName] nvarchar(54) NOT NULL,
    [LastName] nvarchar(54) NOT NULL,
    [Mobile] nvarchar(20) NOT NULL,
    [Email] nvarchar(54) NOT NULL,
    [DateOfBirth] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [CreatedAt] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Customers] PRIMARY KEY ([Id])
);

CREATE TABLE [Todos] (
    [Id] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [Name] nvarchar(54) NOT NULL,
    [Done] bit NOT NULL,
    [CreatedAt] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Todos] PRIMARY KEY ([Id])
);

CREATE TABLE [Users] (
    [Id] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [FirstName] nvarchar(54) NOT NULL,
    [LastName] nvarchar(54) NOT NULL,
    [Email] nvarchar(54) NOT NULL,
    [Password] nvarchar(54) NOT NULL,
    [CreatedAt] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Users] PRIMARY KEY ([Id])
);
